6: WHOO! Are we feeling hyped yet?!
12: Heh, talk about a clueless audience...
17:
It's all good as long as they're
enjoying the event!
28:
Oooh! As Saga idols, Saga Power
burns bright within you!
37:
All right, it's time to put an epic end
to this show by blasting Romero with
Franchouchou's Saga Power!
42: Whaaat? How would we do THAT?!
57:
I can feel the energy welling up from
within... So this is Saga Power!
60:
The producer said to blast it at
Romero-han, but I have no idea how
to do that...
65:
How about we shout at the top of
our lungs together with our fists held
out?
71:
That might work, since we could
pass it off as part of the
performance. What should we shout
though?
76:
We're talking about Saga Power
here, so how about Saga's super
famous... *mumble*
82:
All right. Hold hands, everyone! You
too, Tae-chan!
96:
Thank goodness you're back to
normal, Romero! I'm sorry we left
you alone all this time.
109: Phew, it turned out okay somehow.
131:
We'd better pick up her pieces fast!
Her body's scattered all over!
146:
Ta-dah! Our teamwork put her back
together!
149: Oh, neat. Cool special effects there.
153:
Er... Ahem! Well, that's it for today's
show!
157: Hope you'll continue to support us!
163:
So you girls are zombies, huh? That's
kind of unexpected.
167: Huh, you don't seem very surprised...
170:
We've... had a similar situation
before.
175:
Your scent immediately gave it
away. Humans don't give off that
scent.
179:
You mean you noticed from the
get-go? Yet you kept our cover...
183:
Just didn't see any need to make a
fuss about it.
187:
Anyway, it's a real shocker for the
average person, so you'll probably
still want to keep it a secret in public.
196:
Um, Stella... You know our secret
now, but I hope you'll continue to
support us going forward.
199:
But of course. I look forward to your
next concert as well.
209:
We have Romero back too! It's a
miracle how he got so big!
218:
Consider this our first step to world
domination! We're just getting
started!
229:
Hold on a second... I know
everyone's in a celebratory mood
right now, but we haven't solved
anything.
233:
We still have no clue how to get
back to our world!
237:
Well, of course. We were too focused
on practicing for the concert to
worry about that.
241:
Not like panicking will do us any
good anyhow.
243:
Besides, I wouldn't mind staying in
this world for a bit longer.
249:
Thanks to today's concert,
Franchouchou should now be
known far and wide in this new Saga!
250:
So we're gonna keep it up until we
return to our own Saga! There's your
answer, Sakura!
256:
Gah! Fine! Might as well give it our
all since there's no telling when we'll
be able to return!
261: I look forward to more concerts.
265:
Ahaha, you can bet we'll be
cheering you on all the way. Best of
luck.
271:
Thanks, guys! We're so lucky to have
met you!
